<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1438055>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pericoma miljenkoi Kvifte & Ivković, sp. nov., dissected genitalia. Clockwise from top left: Epandrium, hypandrium, surstylus and proctiger; Aedeagus, parameral sheath and paramere; Gonopod; Apex of surstylus. Scale bar = 100 µm. Abbreviations: bph—basiphallus, b pm—base of paramere, dph—distiphallus, pa b—preapical bristle, phs—phallic sheath, pm—paramere" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1438055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1438053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A. Pericoma miljenkoi Kvifte & Ivković, sp. nov., adult male, head. B. Same, wing." ;
